# Resend Auth

- Generate links via `supabaseAdmin.auth.admin.generateLink()` for signup/magic/reset.
- Send branded emails (React Email) through Resend; routes return 204 (no user enumeration).
- `/auth/callback` establishes session; `/auth/reset` updates password.
